            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台股今早再創新高但後勁不繼，台灣加權指數於早市後段開始倒跌，全日收報37714點，跌164點或0.43%。</p>\n</div>",
